@page "/binformation"

<div class="side-navbar">
    <div class="nav-header">Navigation</div>
    <a href="/bdashboard">Dashboard</a>
    <a href="/bgallery">Gallery</a>
    <a href="/binformation">Information</a>
</div>

<div class="header">
    <h3>Information</h3>
</div>
<div class="card-container">
    <div class="card education-card">
        <h4>Education Program</h4>
        <p>Meow! Hello, lovely human! I'm here to purr-suade you to check out the SPCA's education program...</p>
        <button class="view-btn" onclick="handleButtonClick(event, '/education')">View</button>
    </div>
    <div class="card volunteers-card">
        <h4>Volunteers</h4>
        <p>The SPCA welcomes volunteers with open paws! They’re always looking for big-hearted humans...</p>
        <button class="view-btn" onclick="handleButtonClick(event, '/volunteer')">View</button>
    </div>
    <div class="card pbo-card">
        <h4>We are A PBO</h4>
        <p>Woof Woof hey there, did you know that the SPCA is a PBO (Public Benefit Organization)?...</p>
        <button class="view-btn" onclick="handleButtonClick(event, '/pbo')">View</button>
    </div>
    <div class="card pet-boarding-card">
        <h4>Pet Boarding</h4>
        <p>🐾 Heyy Heyy! The SPCA offers fantastic pet boarding services. They ensure pets are safe and loved...</p>
        <button class="view-btn" onclick="handleButtonClick(event, '/boarding')">View</button>
    </div>
    <div class="card adoption-card">
        <h4>Adoption</h4>
        <p>Hi there! Woof woof! If you're thinking about adding a furry friend to your family, consider adopting...</p>
        <button class="view-btn" onclick="handleButtonClick(event, '/gallery')">View</button>
    </div>
    <div class="card charity-shop-card">
        <h4>Charity Shop</h4>
        <p>The SPCA's charity store is stocked with pet goodies. Visit to find treats, toys, and more while supporting a cause...</p>
        <button class="view-btn" onclick="handleButtonClick(event, '/charityshop')">View</button>
    </div>
    <div class="card sponsors-card">
        <h4>Sponsors and Donations</h4>
        <p>The SPCA relies on donations to keep our tails wagging and purrs loud! Every bit of support counts...</p>
        <button class="view-btn" onclick="handleButtonClick(event, '/donations')">View</button>
    </div>
    <div class="card awareness-card">
        <h4>Animal Welfare Awareness</h4>
        <p>We strive to raise awareness about animal welfare and the importance of responsible pet ownership...</p>
        <button class="view-btn" onclick="handleButtonClick(event, '/awareness')">View</button>
    </div>
    <div class="card events-card">
        <h4>Events</h4>
        <p>Join us for our upcoming events to support animal welfare and have fun while making a difference...</p>
        <button class="view-btn" onclick="handleButtonClick(event, '/events')">View</button>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="loginModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal()">&times;</span>
        <p>Please log in to access this feature.</p>
        <button class="modal-login-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/login'">Login</button>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        background: url('/images/background123.png') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
    }


    .top {
        margin: 30px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .side-navbar {
        height: 100%;
        width: 200px;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        background-color: #143963;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        padding-top: 20px;
        box-shadow: 2px 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        color: white;
    }

        .side-navbar a {
            padding: 15px 20px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

            .side-navbar a:hover {
                background-color: #3e5f8c;
            }

    .header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #143963;
        color: white;
    }

    .card-container {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 15px;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: calc(100% - 200px);
        margin: 0 auto;
        margin-left: 220px;
    }

    .card {
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        background-color: #143963;
        color: white;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

        .card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.03);
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #143963;
        }

    .view-btn {
        padding: 8px 15px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #143963;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 20px;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .view-btn:hover{
        transform: scale(1.03);
            background-color: #143963;
        color: #fff;
    }
    

    .modal {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        z-index: 1;
        left: 0;
        top: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    }

    .modal-content {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        margin: 15% auto;
        padding: 20px;
        width: 300px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .close-btn {
        position: absolute;
        top: 10px;
        right: 15px;
        font-size: 24px;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .modal-login-btn {
        padding: 8px 20px;
        background-color: #143963;
        color: #ffffff;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
</style>

<script>
    const isLoggedIn = false;
    const modal = document.getElementById('loginModal');

    function openModal() {
        modal.style.display = "block";
    }

    function closeModal() {
        modal.style.display = "none";
    }

    function handleButtonClick(event, url) {
        if (!isLoggedIn) {
            event.preventDefault();
            openModal();
        } else {
            window.location.href = url;
        }
    }

    window.onclick = function (event) {
        if (event.target == modal) {
            closeModal();
        }
    }
</script>
